       bn(3), err(3), BN_add(3)

HHIISSTTOORRYY
       BN_add_word() and BN_mod_word() are available in all
       versions of SSLeay and OpenSSL. BN_div_word() was added in
       SSLeay 0.8, and BN_sub_word() and BN_mul_word() in SSLeay
       0.9.0.











